        <section class="mt-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 text-center">Confidence & Strategy Summary</h3>
            <div class="card p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">Based on this comprehensive plan, I am **85% confident** that you will achieve the expected outcomes. The plan is highly targeted, well-researched, and leverages a multi-channel approach to ensure a strong and consistent presence. The only variable is the competitive landscape and the unpredictable nature of lead generation, but the strategies outlined here are designed to maximize your chances of success.</p>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><span class="text-blue-600">1. Hyper-Local SEO & GMB Optimization:</span> This strategy is designed to capture the most valuable, high-intent leads who are searching for "borewell services" specifically in the Hubli and Dharwad areas. By optimizing your GMB profile and website for local keywords, you will rank higher in Google Maps and local search results, directly contributing to your goal of 10th ranking on the website and helping to generate 30 new leads.</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><span class="text-blue-600">2. Multilingual & Culturally Relevant Content:</span> The "Indian touch" is a core strategy for connecting with the local audience. By using relatable themes (festivals like Pitru Paksha, Durga Ashtami, Mysore Dussehra, Gandhi Jayanti, Maharshi Valmiki Jayanti, Deepavali, Karnataka Rajyotsava, Tulsi Vivah, Kanakadasa Jayanti) and local language (Kannada), you build trust and brand affinity. This approach is key to attracting and retaining 40 new social media followers and creating a positive brand image that leads to a higher conversion rate.</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><span class="text-blue-600">3. Targeted Paid Advertising (Google & Meta):</span> This is a dual-pronged approach to lead generation. Google Ads captures immediate demand from people ready to buy, while Meta Ads build long-term brand awareness and capture leads who are still in the consideration phase. This balance ensures a steady flow of inquiries and is the primary driver for achieving your goal of 30 new leads for the provided ad budget.</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><span class="text-blue-600">4. Integrated Outreach Campaigns:</span> The telecalling and WhatsApp campaigns are a direct and effective way to generate immediate interest and appointments. The scripts are designed to be concise and lead-focused. The IVR system ensures that incoming calls are routed efficiently, preventing lost opportunities. This strategy is specifically tailored to meet your goals of 20 good appointment interests and 5 fixed appointments.</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800"><span class="text-blue-600">5. Authority Building through Content Marketing:</span> The detailed website content, including blogs, case studies, and a strong "About Us" page, is not just for SEO; it's for building credibility. By showcasing expertise and providing valuable information, you establish your company as a trusted authority. This long-term strategy will result in higher search engine rankings and more trust from potential customers, leading to organic leads and a strong foundation for acquiring 10 Google reviews and long-term business growth.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
